_:N8480cc4cf0ed45648ff19b5546c0f1a7 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Mark Tami was appointed Treasurer of His Majesty’s Household (Deputy Chief Whip) on 10 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>He was elected as the MP for Alyn and Deeside in July 2024.</p>\n\n" .
